Description: Recreational Fisheries Information Network
    ([RecFIN](https://www.recfin.org/) is a joint effort guided by the
    Pacific States Marine Fisheries Commission to sample recreational
    fishing.  This R package, RecFIN, is meant to work with the sampled
    data.
